  <a href="index.html">← Back</a>
  <h1>Fresh Fettuccine Alfredo</h1>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>10–12 oz fettuccine</li>
    <li>4 tbsp butter</li>
    <li>1 cup heavy cream</li>
    <li>1–1½ cups grated Parmesan</li>
    <li>Salt + black pepper</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Boil salted water; cook pasta. Save 1 cup pasta water and drain.</li>
    <li>Melt butter on low; add cream and warm gently.</li>
    <li>Stir in Parmesan until smooth.</li>
    <li>Toss pasta in sauce; loosen with pasta water if needed.</li>
    <li>Season and serve.</li>
  </ol>
